text: Yang Gwang-jae (born 1 July 1965) is a South Korean rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
